title: Nissan car sales in Europe 2003 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of units sold. In total the number of data points it has is 16.
In general Number of units sold has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of units sold, about 560415.0 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Number of units sold about 313437.0 was reached at Year 2007
